PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1996-1201 of August 7, 1996 which reappointed the HONOURABLE ROBERT CARMAN COATES as a permanent member of the Canadian International Trade Tribunal, by revoking the words "ending August 21, 1997" and substituting the words "ending December 31, 1997".
